{"word":"G1338 - διϊκνέομαι - diïknéomai - dee-ik-neh'-om-ahee - Pierce","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διϊκνέομαι</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">diïknéomai</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dee-ik-neh'-om-ahee</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Pierce</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - உருவக்குத்து"},{"paragraph":"to go through, penetrate, pierce"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1223 - διά - diá - dee-ah'/1223\">G1223</a> and the base of <a href=\"#/G2425 - ἱκανός - hikanós - hik-an-os'/2425\">G2425</a>; to <i>reach through</i>, that is, <i>penetrate:</i> - pierce.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}